name: Meetingscheduler
tagline: Spring Boot, Spring Data Rest and Angular JS to perform CRUD operations against Scheduling a Meeting and blocking a Room
body:
### Welcome to Meeting Scheduler.
This is a Single Page Application aimed at Scheduling a Corporate meeting.  
Technology Stack: Spring Boot, Spring Data Rest, AngularJS, Maven

### Templates

**https://localhost:8080/home**

Click button Schedule Meeting
